{"id": "art-25123", "label": "Art. 25123", "title": "Art. 25123", "slug": "art-25123", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1661542372\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1706\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1661542372\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>23</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2068355376\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1705\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2068355376\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În sensul\nprezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>, fuziunea\ntransfrontalier&#259; este <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> prin\ncare:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_841606105\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1704\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_841606105\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)una sau mai multe <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\ndintre cele enumerate în anexa II a Directivei (UE) </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>2017/1.132</span><span style='color:black'>, dintre care\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> dou&#259; sunt guvernate de <span\nclass=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> a dou&#259; state membre diferite, sunt\ndizolvate f&#259;r&#259; a intra în lichidare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ntransfer&#259; totalitatea activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivelor lor unei alte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> în\nschimbul repartiz&#259;rii c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nabsorbite de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social la societatea\nabsorbant&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, eventual, al unei <span\nclass=SpellE>pl&#259;&#355;i</span> în numerar de maximum 10% din valoarea\nnominal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social astfel\nrepartizate; sau</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_196105639\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1703\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_196105639\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)mai multe <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\ndintre cele enumerate în anexa II a Directivei (UE) </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>2017/1.132</span><span style='color:black'>, dintre care\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> dou&#259; sunt guvernate de <span\nclass=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> a dou&#259; state membre diferite, sunt\ndizolvate f&#259;r&#259; a intra în lichidare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ntransfer&#259; totalitatea activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivelor lor unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> pe care o\nconstituie, în schimbul repartiz&#259;rii c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nlor de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span>\nsociale sau alte titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social la societatea\nnou-constituit&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, eventual, al unei <span\nclass=SpellE>pl&#259;&#355;i</span> în numerar de maximum 10% din valoarea\nnominal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social astfel\nrepartizate;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1486301954\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1702\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1486301954\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)o societate, dintre cele enumerate în anexa II a\nDirectivei (UE) </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>2017/1.132</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, este dizolvat&#259; f&#259;r&#259; a intra în lichidare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> transfer&#259; totalitatea activelor <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivelor sale unei alte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\nguvernate de <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> altui stat membru, care <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span> totalitatea <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nsale, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sale sociale sau a altor\ntitluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2081388669\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1701\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2081388669\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)una sau mai multe <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\ndintre cele enumerate în anexa II a Directivei (UE) </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>2017/1.132</span><span style='color:black'>, <span\nclass=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> transfer&#259;, ca urmare a dizolv&#259;rii\nf&#259;r&#259; lichidare, toate activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\npasivele unei alte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> existente,\nsocietatea absorbant&#259;, f&#259;r&#259; emiterea de noi <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social de c&#259;tre societatea absorbant&#259;, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span> ca o persoan&#259; s&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;</span> direct sau indirect totalitatea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care fuzioneaz&#259; sau cu <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span> ca <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> care fuzioneaz&#259; s&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social în <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>propor&#355;ie</span> în toate <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncare fuzioneaz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_231541030\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1700\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_231541030\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Plata în numerar poate fi superioar&#259; valorii\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. a) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> b),\ndac&#259; cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> <span class=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span>\nunuia dintre statele membre a c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>na&#355;ionalitate</span>\no <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nparticipante la fuziune sau societatea nou-constituit&#259; permite <span\nclass=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;irea</span> acestui procent.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_832608702\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1699\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_832608702\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA\n2:Etape. Efecte. Nulitate</span></b></p>"}